text"> OAuth2 的授權模式</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A%E7%A2%BC%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6"><span class="toc-number">3.2.1.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 授權碼模式測試</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F"><span class="toc-number">3.2.2.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 密碼模式</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#jwt%E4%BB%A4%E7%89%8C"><span class="toc-number">4.</span> <span class="toc-text"> JWT 令牌</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E4%BB%A4%E7%89%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C"><span class="toc-number">4.1.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 普通令牌的問題</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AFjwt"><span class="toc-number">4.2.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 什么是 JWT</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#243-%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E7%94%A2%E7%94%9Fjwt%E4%BB%A4%E7%89%8C"><span class="toc-number">4.3.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 2.4.3 測試產生 JWT 令牌</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%B6%B2%E9%97%9C%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89"><span class="toc-number">4.4.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 網關認證</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE%E7%B6%B2%E9%97%9C%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89"><span class="toc-number">4.5.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 實現網關認證</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89"><span class="toc-number">5.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 用户認證</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E9%80%A3%E7%B5%90%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E5%BA%AB"><span class="toc-number">5.1.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 連結用戶中心資料庫</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%93%B4%E5%B1%95%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A"><span class="toc-number">5.1.1.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 擴展用戶身份資訊</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E8%B3%87%E6%BA%90%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD"><span class="toc-number">5.1.2.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 資源服務取得使用者身份</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%9A%E6%A8%A3"><span class="toc-number">6.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 支援認證方式多樣</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%B5%B1%E4%B8%80%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%A3"><span class="toc-number">6.1.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 統一認證入口</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%AF%A6%E7%8F%BE%E5%B8%B3%E8%99%9F%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%89"><span class="toc-number">6.2.</span> <span class="toc-text"> 實現帳號密碼認證</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></div><div class="related panel pjax" data-title="系列文章"><ul><li  class="active"><a href="/John/2023/10/30/java/SpringSecurity/SpringSecurity" rel="bookmark" title="SpringSecurity 認證授權">SpringSecurity 認證授權</a></li><li ><a href="/John/2023/11/03/java/SpringSecurity/WeChat_login" rel="bookmark" title="SpringSecurity 微信登錄">SpringSecurity 微信登錄</a></li></ul></div><div class="overview panel" data-title="本站概要"><div class="author" itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><img class="image" itemprop="image" alt="John" data-src="/John/assets/404.png"/><p class="name" itemprop="name">John</p><div class="description" itemprop="description"></div></div><nav class="state"><div class="item posts"><a href="/John/archives/"><span class="co